verbose_text: In particular, the examination of the blood content after intragastric in vivo administration of aqueous suspensions of PSi and LA-Si NPs into rats in dosages of 0.7 mg/kg and 4.9 mg/kg did not cause any statistically significant changes in blood levels of aminotrasferases, alkaline phosphatase, bilirubin and cholesterol (see details in Section 6 of XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), which gave evidence for the absence of side effects.
